  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/13e9c8f83ad6489db61d85a3c6210727.avif?t=1614267767\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br>Which of you is the most erudite? Do you think that you know a certain topic better than your friends? Welcome to Dummy! Here you can find out whether you really believe in yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/810d6ea2a9d2b107c661651afcebb022.avif?t=1614267767\" width=550 height=73 /></span><br>Gather a group of friends for up to 10 people, choose the interesting question pack with the necessary topics and compete, collecting points that will bring you victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/15faf65d8d98623dfdb02b8ff03d6225.avif?t=1614267767\" width=550 height=73 /></span><br>Create question packs. An intuitive editor for creating questions will allow you to create really interesting topics! Then share the questions you created with other players in the Steam Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/9044290c5331822ca2c576744d82b5d6.avif?t=1614267767\" width=550 height=73 /></span><br>Find rivals online. There will always be a person who will put your knowledge into question!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/13e9c8f83ad6489db61d85a3c6210727.avif?t=1614267767\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br>Which of you is the most erudite? Do you think that you know a certain topic better than your friends? Welcome to Dummy! Here you can find out whether you really believe in yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/810d6ea2a9d2b107c661651afcebb022.avif?t=1614267767\" width=550 height=73 /></span><br>Gather a group of friends for up to 10 people, choose the interesting question pack with the necessary topics and compete, collecting points that will bring you victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/15faf65d8d98623dfdb02b8ff03d6225.avif?t=1614267767\" width=550 height=73 /></span><br>Create question packs. An intuitive editor for creating questions will allow you to create really interesting topics! Then share the questions you created with other players in the Steam Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754480/extras/9044290c5331822ca2c576744d82b5d6.avif?t=1614267767\" width=550 height=73 /></span><br>Find rivals online. There will always be a person who will put your knowledge into question!",
